description.en: The objective of the Machine Learning Test Ontology (MiLTO) is to model machine learning test procedures and their associated data. The main objective of this study is to characterize failures in machine learning tools, especially TensorFlow information about systems and users. This ontology is based on doctoral research carried out at IME-USP.

comments.en: An ontology to describe the testing process in machine learning tools and describe how failures occur in these systems. The work was done by Alexandre Locci Martins and Ana Cristina Vierira de Melo.
